T12:58:04.000Z","msg":"但係好多人都係真心ge<br />\n針唔吉到唔知痛呢"},{"pid":"dd4b364eb32ba5fb48d053c27a0401d654c717bf","tid":1626740,"uid":93451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果學校範圍唔算公眾地方 <br />\n聽日一齊返學校有無得諗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都認為聽日係和理非回合[url][/url]<br />\n想出去表達 打下條國際線<br />\n但揾唔到一個一開始同最後唔比人清場嘅方法<br />\n但如果我地帶口罩係大學<br />\n校友\b,大學生,中學生 仲有唔同年齡愛香港嘅香港人<br />\n一齊進行學術討論討論下香港又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n純粹諗到想討論下可行性<br />\n可能時間係好趕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但聽日最緊要係做到野 同安全</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地好耐無新嘅創意啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果八大有好多香港人坐晒係到<br />\n帶口罩表達自己意見<br />\n我覺得個畫面會同二百萬人一樣咁好睇</span></span></strong></span><br />\n最好有法律巴絲入黎分析下<br />\n一齊入黎討論下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626652/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626652/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"26c7afc08658b14750c4a29eeff7cc9b077de2d4","tid":1626740,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"你即刻同佢地表白 咁佢地就唔會驚困入集中營"},{"pid":"636c613e122c514517560e800578f0cc913f0fc5","tid":1626740,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26c7afc08658b14750c4a29eeff7cc9b077de2d4","tid":1626740,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"你即刻同佢地表白 咁佢地就唔會驚困入集中營"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"痴線..."},{"pid":"d4bbb00b711f7e563521dbf7f5c3ceb814c7d4b3","tid":1626740,"uid":216044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"就係因為大家都驚呢件事遲早會發生，所以先咁出力去阻止"},{"pid":"00056251ebace97513a5389022592308427dce37","tid":1626740,"uid":324701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"叫佢㩒錢<img src=\"/assets/face